<i>I'm afraid you're going to have</i>
<i>to do better, Doctor.</i>

47
00:02:48,293 --> 00:02:50,295
Yeah, give us a break,
Doctor.

48
00:02:50,378 --> 00:02:55,216
RIVIERA: <i>But Troy,</i>
<i>how can I make it lower than $39.95?</i>

49
00:02:55,300 --> 00:02:57,135
MCCLURE:
<i>Find a way.</i>

50
