Hey, Homer, I can't find
the safety goggles for the power saw.

51
00:02:59,470 --> 00:03:01,556
If stuff starts flying,
just turn your head.

52
00:03:01,639 --> 00:03:02,932
Aw, check.

53
00:03:03,016 --> 00:03:04,934
